Subject: [PATCH 3/9] codex: add favicon set

---
 CODEX-REPORT.md |   1 +
 favicon.ico     | Bin 0 -> 8515 bytes
 index.html      |   1 +
 sw.js           |   3 ++-
 4 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)
 create mode 100644 favicon.ico

diff --git a/CODEX-REPORT.md b/CODEX-REPORT.md
index 93babe8..6884fa6 100644
--- a/CODEX-REPORT.md
+++ b/CODEX-REPORT.md
@@ -4,3 +4,4 @@
 | --- | --- | --- | --- |
 | 1 - Image regeneration pass | `CODEX-REPORT.md` | PASS - `node scripts/qa-check.js pwa`; PASS - `node scripts/qa-check.js` | Reviewed asset contact sheet at `/private/tmp/sticker-swap-assets-task1.jpg`. Existing 18 WebP assets are visually consistent at mobile size, under 150 KB each, and contain no baked-in text, so no regeneration was needed. `npm` is unavailable in this shell, so the equivalent underlying Node QA command was run directly. |
 | 2 - og-share.png rebuild | `og-share.png`, `sw.js`, `CODEX-REPORT.md` | PASS - `node scripts/qa-check.js` | Rebuilt 1200x630 OG image with gold headline, white subline, right-side sticker-card art, and muted disclaimer. Output is about 136 KB. Bumped service-worker cache from v6 to v7 because `og-share.png` is in `APP_SHELL`. |
+| 3 - Favicon set | `favicon.ico`, `index.html`, `sw.js`, `CODEX-REPORT.md` | PASS - `node scripts/qa-check.js` | Added 16/32/48 favicon, inserted ICO link before SVG icon link, added favicon to `APP_SHELL`, and bumped cache from v7 to v8. SVG raster tooling was unavailable, so ICO was generated from the matching 512px PNG mark. |
diff --git a/favicon.ico b/favicon.ico
new file mode 100644
